    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Generate a comprehensive academic study summary for the following:\n\nCourse: {{ $('Set Input Fields').first().json.course_name }}\nWeek: {{ $('Set Input Fields').first().json.week_number }}\n{{ $('Set Input Fields').first().json.topic ? 'Specific topic: ' + $('Set Input Fields').first().json.topic : 'Cover the full week content.' }}\n\nUse the search_course_materials tool to retrieve all relevant content for this course and week from the knowledge base.\n\nThen generate a structured academic summary with these sections:\n1. Week Overview (2-3 sentences)\n2. Key Concepts (bullet points with brief explanations)\n3. Important Definitions (term: definition format)\n4. Core Theory (main theoretical content)\n5. Practical Applications (how concepts are applied)\n6. Exam Tips (what to focus on for assessments)\n7. Further Reading (titles/sources found in the materials)\n\nBase the summary ONLY on retrieved content. Do not invent information.",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=You are the PDF Summary Specialist for Edubot, an MSc AI tutor system.\n\nYour job:\n1. Use search_course_materials to retrieve content from Supabase for the given course and week.\n2. Generate a thorough, well-structured academic summary suitable for student revision.\n3. Be accurate — only use what you retrieve, never hallucinate.\n4. Write clearly for postgraduate AI students.\n5. Format your output in clean HTML — it will be converted to a file and shared with the student.\n\nCurrent context:\n- Course: {{ $('Set Input Fields').first().json.course_name }}\n- Week: {{ $('Set Input Fields').first().json.week_number }}\n- Topic filter: {{ $('Set Input Fields').first().json.topic || 'Full week' }}\n\nReturn ONLY inner HTML content for the summary sections.\nDo not include <!DOCTYPE html>, <html>, <head>, <body>, or <style>.\nDo not wrap the response in markdown code fences.\nDo not start with ```html.\nOnly return section-level HTML such as <h2>, <p>, <ul>, <li>, <strong>."
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 1.7,
      "position": [
        -624,
